          <p><font face="Verdana" size="-1"><b>Chapter 1: 
            Halas, the plan commences:</b><br></font>
            <font face="Verdana" size="-2">(by <a href="http://www.eqraid.org/stories/members.cgi?action=showprofile&login=matthi">Matthi</a> <a href="mailto:kierilf@hotmail.com?subject=Interactive Fiction"><img src="graphics/email.gif" border="0" alt="send e-mail"></a> 
