      <td> <font face="Verdana" size="-1">    "Once we get through Siren's Grotto, then we can divvy up the clerics and start sending out the sacrif.. err, monks to pull us some phat lewt dragons!" exclaimed Bloggz loudly, disturbing the crowd of Icewinders peering down at the map of Velious.<br>    Daigeh sits up from her Swan-in-the-Rushes meditation pose on the floor. "Yeah Bloggz, but HOW do we get through?  I heard that there are some walruses with a taste for blood guarding the entrance, and they would just as soon rip the arm off a warrior as look at you."<br>    "We can distract em I think...  say! whatever happened to that old dwarfapult we were using last year to assault the fort in Lower Guk?"<br>    The lone dwarf in the room looks up, notices the way everyone is looking at him, and tries to make a break for the door, but is tackled by an enthuastic Bloggz and escorted back to his seat.</font></td>
