      <td> <font face="Verdana" size="-1">"Ambrose!" exclaimed Daigeh jubilantly, "we have a job PERFECT for you!".  Ambrose looks around suspiciously, while suspended from Bloggz's meaty paw.  "Last time this happened, I lost my beer midflight!" Ambrose said miserably.<br><br>Temporal stops mezzing all the occupants in CIW's resident ant farm, and looks up morosely.  "You know, we could strap him to a keg of beer before launching him.  We'll have to stick a plastic tube into one end and shove the other end into his pie hole." Temporal said.<br><br>Ambrose's eyebrows raise in alarm and delight at the same time.  "Hmmm, I get a whole keg to myself?" Ambrose asked?  Stifling a chuckle, Daigeh announced "So it's settled, strap dorf23... err Ambrose to a keg, and lets launch em at the target!"<br><br></font></td>
